ountNumber =3D accountNumber;\n    this.balance =3D 0.0;\n  }\n\n  public v=
oid deposit(double amount) {\n    if (amount > 0) {\n      balance +=3D amo=
unt;\n    }\n  }\n\n  public double getBalance() {\n    return balance;\n  =
}\n}\n```\n\n### Beispiel 2: Vererbung in einem Zoo-Management-System\n\nIm=
 Kontext eines Zoo-Management-Systems kann die Vererbung dazu verwendet wer=
