wingSpan) {\n    super(name, age, species);\n    this.wingSpan =3D wingSpan=
;\n  }\n\n  @Override\n  public void makeSound() {\n    System.out.println(=
name + \&quot; says Tweet\&quot;);\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### Beispiel 3: Polymorp=
