n    this.accountNumber =3D accountNumber;\n    this.balance =3D 0.0;\n  }\=
n\n  public void deposit(double amount) {\n    if (amount > 0) {\n      bal=
ance +=3D amount;\n    }\n  }\n\n  public double getBalance() {\n    return=
 balance;\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### Beispiel 2: Vererbung in einem Zoo-Management=
